To say VulpineFace:
	if Perception of Mistress Snuggle >= 1 and Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 0:
		say "graced with a long, tapered canine [one of]snout[or]snoot[or]muzzle[at random], thin black lips, and sharp predatory ivory teeth. Despite their brilliant nacre gleam of your fangs, your soft matronly smile, and cute button nose puts all but the most jaded people at ease. Your slitted [if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 0]exotic magenta[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 1]verdant emerald[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 2]deep azure[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 3]stunning ruby red[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 4]phosphorescent pink[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 5]luminous gold[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 6]deep brown[end if] eyes only add to the illusion, as more than a few fair souls have almost themselves in their wondrous depths. ";
		say "Perched atop your foxy head are a pair of [if Stamina of Mistress Snuggle is 0]unusually large canidae ears, while nowhere near as prominent as a fennec's. Their stature helps you stand out in a crowd without inconveniencing you[else if Stamina of Mistress Snuggle is 1]modest canine with cute little patches of fur on their tips[else if Stamina of Mistress Snuggle is 2]large fennec ears. Though at times their size can be just a touch annoying, sounds have never been clearer and their natural cooling properties are more than welcome on some of the warmer days[end if][if Morale of Mistress Snuggle is 1]. Nestled between your ears, you have a striking set of long ivory white swept back reminiscent of some great draconic creature[else if Morale of Mistress Snuggle is 2]. A set of cute little black demonic horns shaped like many of the succubi wandering the city protrude from your forehead[else if Morale of Mistress Snuggle is 3]. Sprouting out the top of your forehead is a set of long branching bourbon brown deer horns, leading an added air of primal majesty to adorable your visage[else if Morale of Mistress Snuggle is 4]. Curling around the side of your forehead are a thick set of burnished brown goat horns[end if]";
	else if Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle >= 1 and Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 0:
		say "elongated into a sleek, proud vulpine muzzle with glossy ebony lips and large intimidating fangs. For all your bestial splendor and noticable cocksure grin, more then few curious souls are still drawn by in by the wondrous shimmer of your slitted [if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 0]magenta[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 1]emerald green[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 2]azure blue[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 3]ruby red[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 4]phosphorescent pink[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 5]luminous gold[else if Intelligence of Mistress Snuggle is 6]deep chestnut brown[end if] eyes glittering in [if daytimer is day]the sunlight[else if daytimer is night]the starlight[end if]. Perch atop your vulpine head are a ";
		say "[if Stamina of Mistress Snuggle is 0]unusually large canidae ears, while nowhere near as prominent as a fennec's. Their stature helps you stand out in a crowd without inconveniencing you[else if Stamina of Mistress Snuggle is 1]modest canine with cute little patches of fur on their tips[else if Stamina of Mistress Snuggle is 2]large fennec ears. Though at times their size can be just a touch annoying, sounds have never been clearer and their natural cooling properties are more than welcome on some of the warmer days[end if]. [if Morale of Mistress Snuggle is 1]Nestled between your ears, you have a striking set of long ivory white swept back reminiscent of some great draconic creature[else if Morale of Mistress Snuggle is 2]A set of cute little black demonic horns shaped like many of the succubi wandering the city protrude from your forehead[else if Morale of Mistress Snuggle is 3]Sprouting out the top of your forehead is a set of long branching bourbon brown deer horns, leading an added air of primal majesty to adorable your visage[else if Morale of Mistress Snuggle is 4]Curling around the side of your forehead are a thick set of burnished brown goat horns[end if]";

