		say "The supple padding swaddling your cute mummy tummy spills out along your limbs, outwardly soft and just the right kind of jiggle. Tilting your head for a better look, you find your our pillowy extremities more than match your motherly disposition. Although as you flex your budding paws, you can still detect the hardened layer of animalist muscle buried beneath your cuddly floof. All the better to carry you[if player is impreg_now], and your cubs[end if][if depravity of Mistress Snuggle >= 1]. You crow, flexing your talon in curious elation as the last sputtering vestiges of change pool along your shoulder blades. Your hide begins to bulge, then fan outwards, forming[end if][if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 1] a lustrous set of simmering alabaster wings coated in downy feathers[else if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 2] a regal set of large, intimidating draconic wings bejeweled in glittering scales[else if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 3] a small pair of adorable bat wings swaddled in velvety fur and glossy black skin[else if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 4] an octet of graceful ebony tendrils[end if]";
	else if Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 3 and Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 0: [very chubby]
