	else if Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 4 and Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 0: [ultra husky]
		say "you huff in anticipation of your impending changes. You can already feel the vast stores of vulpine essence billowing to the surface of your [bodyname of player] body as a luxurious tide of tallow billows across your belly and [bodydesc of Player] flanks, subsuming any gross, unsightly muscle beyond a welcome veil of opulent sensual softness. Grinning from ear-to-ear, your hands gleefully roam your precious belly and wondrous womb, groping gleeful handfuls of downy pudge as the dense protective layer of hand swallowing opulence flows over your elated figure. Stars you missed this so much, you purr, observing the tender tide of excesses crest your arms, as heavy pillows of motherly padding creep down your shoulders, swaddling your limbs in velvety adipose. Only to stop scant inches from palms as they begin to writhe amidst the squall transformative energy while they shift once more into their pleasing vulpine shape complete with cute heart-shaped pads. Overjoyed by the familiar feeling, you lovingly run their fetching dainty forms southward along your fertile hips to the ripening swell of your changing legs. ";
		say "Though the regal dusting of matronly fluffy buries much of your changes beneath its pillowy splendor, the feeling power and purpose coursing through your limbs is utterly intoxicating as your legs crackle and contort into their sublimely cushioned vulpine bend[if depravity of Mistress Snuggle >= 1]. You crow, flexing your talon in curious elation as the last sputtering vestiges of change pool along your shoulder blades. Your hide begins to bulge, then fan outwards, forming[end if][if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 1] a lustrous set of simmering alabaster wings coated in downy feathers[else if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 2] a regal set of large, intimidating draconic wings bejeweled in glittering scales[else if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 3] a small pair of adorable bat wings swaddled in velvety fur and glossy black skin[else if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 4] an octet of graceful ebony tendrils[end if]";
	else if Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 5 and Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 0: [Overfed demi-blob]
		say "you mewl in lewd delectation as the roiling ocean of vulpine essence slumbering inside you bubbles once more to the surface. Your being sloshes and churns as a welcome plume of cuddly tallow ripples across your once [bodydesc of Player] enveloping your middle in wondrous foxy opulence. Another time, you might have felt a hint of fear of disquiet at the sight of your ponderous belly spilling out before you in a vast arm swallowing mountain of pillowy pudge and maternal splendor. Yet now, your tainted-mind swoons at the hypnotic jiggle of your monumental middle, or the sweltering heat of love handles hugging your arms as they blossom to the doughy slabs of matronly perfection they were meant to be. You muse, affectionately drawing your cute heart-shaped pads along your changing legs in raw elation at regal softness spreading over them. While much of their definition is obscured beneath your luxuriant thunder thighs, your twisting psyche still wallows in the vibrant sparks of primal power building in your legs. As the hidden layer of dense muscle swirling into being along their digitigrade contours, true you can't really see the changes, behind the supple dome of your mammoth tum, but the feeling remains ";
