		say "Yet as the spastic crests your wrist, your extremities begin to shift as your palms and soles of your thicken while they rapidly reform into glossy pink canine pads. All the while, your nails darken, then migrate towards the end of your digits as they grow into sharp glossy black vulpine talons. [if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 1] You crow, flexing your bladed digits in curious elation as the last sputtering vestiges of change pool along your shoulder blades. Your hide begins to bulge, then fan outwards, forming a lustrous set of simmering alabaster wings coated in downy feathers [else]Giving them an experimental flex, your sense of balance slowly returns as your tainted body swiftly acclimatizes to your latest change[end if]";
	else if Dexterity of Mistress Snuggle is 2 and Perception of Mistress Snuggle is 0: [Athletic]
		say "you find yourself breaking into a sudden roiling fever, sweat and steam pour off of you in a velvety alabaster plume as traces of adipose or unnecessary tissue is subsumed behind a dense coating of lean, potent muscle. Rather fetching to the eye, you playfully run your hands along your toned core in admiration of steely sinew greeting your mitts as you explore the pleasant tightness of your athletic middle. Your hips begin to expand with tasteful buxom curves and just the barest hints of feminine padding along the gentle contours of your once [bodydesc of Player] ass. Rather pleased by the sight, you give your tush a playful little slap just to marvel at its firmness while the changes spread outward to your limbs. As your legs twist into a more familiar sculpted vulpine bend, accustomed to the change in balance, the feeling of your weight shifting the edges of your foxy toes is almost natural to you now. You muse, tilting your legs for a better view as you observe the lustrous alteration of your feet into proper canine paws graced with soft mushy pink toe beans and sleek claws. All the while, the changes begin to creep over your arms as your biceps bulge ever-so-slightly with rich sculpted hills of primal sinew and hands grow sweltering hot. As your mitts grow cushy pink pads and adorable glossy beans, capped by prominent canine talons that seem to glitter like polished onyx in the light[if depravity of Mistress Snuggle is 1]. You crow, flexing your bladed digits in curious elation as the last sputtering vestiges of change pool along your shoulder blades. Your hide begins to bulge, then fan outwards, forming a lustrous set of simmering alabaster wings coated in downy feathers[end if]";
